  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::FTUEManager
  fTUECanvas: {fileID: 0}
  tutorialText: {fileID: 0}
  nextButtonText: {fileID: 0}
  tutorialTexts:
  - Welcome to\n <size=200%>Click and Buy</size>
  - Issue a "Buy" trade when price is low and you think it will go up.
  - Issue a "Sell" trade when price is high and you think it will go down.
  - Active trades are displayed in the panel below.
  - Click "Close Trade" (right most button in active trades) to lock in profits and
    return your initial investment.
  - If a trade performs badly and loses more than your initial investment, your cash
    reserves will cover the loss.\n\nIf a loss is big enough and there's no more
    cash on hand, the losing trade will auto-close and you will lose all invested
    money from that trade (Risk Meter).
  - Reach 1M$ to Win!\n\nGood Luck.
  fadeInTextFeedback: {fileID: 8776301748097169142}
  currentTextIndex: 0
